{{Quote|When our rangers found Arson Iceaxe picking away at the Wall, he was almost halfway through. The rangers decided not to disturb him and sealed the way behind him with ice and stone and snow. Some say if you press your ear flat to the Wall, you can still hear Arson chipping away with his axe.|[[Samwell Tarly]]|The Wall (Histories &amp; Lore)}}
'''Arson''', also known as '''Arson Iceaxe''', is an unseen character in ''[[Game of Thrones (TV series)|Game of Thrones]]''. He is long dead when the series begins.
